' cursor-default' : ' cursor-zoom-out' }`} > )} {videoSrc! && ( isDesktop && e.stopPropagation()} layoutId={`video-${videoSrc}`} className={`" w-fit h-[80%] mx-auto ${ isDesktop ? ' cursor-default' : ' cursor-zoom-out' }`} > )} )} {imgSrc! && ( { setIsMediaModalOpen(true) }} layoutId={`img-${imgSrc}`} className={cn('overflow-hidden w-full', className)} > )} {videoSrc! && ( { setIsMediaModalOpen(true) }} layoutId={`video-${videoSrc}`} className={cn('overflow-hidden w-full h-full', className)} > )} ) } ```
